fr.gouv.finances.dgfip.xemelios.auth

Interface XemeliosUser

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SimpleXemeliosUserImpl

    public interface XemeliosUser
    Carries user's properties. If an implementation carries user's password, it must be encrypted, but its better not to keep password in instance.
